{"tid":959904,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"肥花：【用家：難怪美國咁驚】Huawei Mate 20 心得","createTime":"2018-12-29T03:45:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-01T08:51:25.000Z","uid":147376,"like":8,"dislike":89,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"a8e32c2b09fe30018d26d3b6e96871ac96cb4686","tid":959904,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T03:45:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.dcfever.com/news/readnews.php?id=24048\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcfever.com%2Fnews%2Freadnews.php%3Fid%3D24048&d=6lR%2Beu03msxNISXeKu7jm10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=12a35a5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dcfever.com/news/readnews.php?id=24048</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHuawei 今年的成績有目共睹，P20 Pro 成 DxOMark 最強攝力手機，<span style=\"color: red;\">叫好叫座</span>，幫助 Huawei 出貨量首次超越 Apple，成為市場「二哥」。新旗艦 Huawei Mate 20 究竟值不值得繼而支持？<span style=\"color: red;\">大家可以從本網中肯的用家心得了解一下。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ih9k6aN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fih9k6aN.jpg&h=cb52672c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DJj9e38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDJj9e38.jpg&h=6d61b1a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屏幕大、拍攝效果好、電量使用時間長<br />\n不少用家都對 Huawei Mate 20 的 6.53 吋屏幕十分喜愛，屏幕比 iPhone XS MAX 更大，手持使用不覺太大部；拍攝效果出色，而且支援超廣角、微距及無損變焦拍攝功能，拍攝玩法十分全面；一般情況下使用，大部份用家都能支撐一天，使用時間持久，都是 Mate 20 的優點。<span style=\"color: red;\">用家還希望大家不要對國產手機有偏見，以 Mate 20 的表現優於 iPhone XS MAX，但定價低一半，難怪美國會怕中國發展科技發展。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OY4AU4k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOY4AU4k.jpg&h=6d04612d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SVG7Ma1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSVG7Ma1.jpg&h=8b2af8c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自拍修飾過度、專用記憶咭有點貴、防水效能一般<br />\n用家主要都給予 Huawei Mate 20 正面評價，但難免亦有一些需要改善的地方，如自拍時修飾過度，拍得自己「太靚仔」不夠自然；專用記憶咭 nano Memory 定價有點兒貴，另外機身只有 IP53 防水規格，防水效能未算出色，都是 Mate 20 的小小缺點。"},{"pid":"1de890d3f4f7c78d1e24c6a6ee00bc0aeacf2c54","tid":959904,"uid":81113,"like":73,"dislike":2,"score":71,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T03:48:01.000Z","msg":"咁你買左未？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NEcPGBQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNEcPGBQ.gif&h=24101285&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a56594baa1cddf1d262022637909e8bf228ee623","tid":959904,"uid":191352,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T03:50:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1696f725829e8a49ec6adb91a92b51003eda1374","tid":959904,"uid":37524,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"a56594baa1cddf1d262022637909e8bf228ee623","tid":959904,"uid":191352,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"1de890d3f4f7c78d1e24c6a6ee00bc0aeacf2c54","tid":959904,"uid":81113,"like":73,"dislike":2,"score":71,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T03:48:01.000Z","msg":"咁你買左未？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NEcPGBQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNEcPGBQ.gif&h=24101285&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T03:50:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T03:50:46.000Z","msg":"解放軍新兵器"},{"pid":"6e5410d77a31bb1d1e737c7279bb16bad38ff349","tid":959904,"uid":147376,"like":5,"dislike":32,"score":-27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T03:52:56.000Z","msg":"所謂嘅中立意見<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UhuxcTM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUhuxcTM.png&h=80852d62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NkrojyO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNkrojyO.png&h=2a1e37a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TD2rhks.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTD2rhks.png&h=0b358d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c97ee94b6e83e70ba0cc2c69a3802bede020db